[Student "S"]
{When WEST agrees to \Ss, EAST will not stop short of a slam. 
The RKCB 4NT bid tells EAST that they have all five Key Cards since WEST could hardly 
have a 2\C opening hand with no Aces.

EAST's 5\H bid is the Queen Ask, and WEST's reply confirms that she holds 
the \SQ, and also has the \CK.

EAST figures the \S suit will run, and this should be enough for Grand Slam. He chooses 7NT.}

